#: ../../../release_details/9.5/htg-representation-decimation.md:1
msgid "HTG Surface Representation improvements"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.5/htg-representation-decimation.md:3
msgid ""
"Cells outside the camera frustum are now decimated in 3D as well as 1D and "
"2D in HTG Surface Representation. The method to check their visibility has "
"been generified to work in all cases, including without parallel projection "
"(which was required before), and with masks. Existing tests have been "
"updated and new ones created to cover these functionalities."
msgstr ""

